text: Ðis syndon ðæs landesgemæru æt Grimanleage.
Ærest of Seferne be higna gemære on sceacan halh & swa be þære alra ofesce in ða neowan dic.
And swa up ondlang þære neowan dic þæt on þa aldan hegestowe.
And syððan a andlang þære ealdan hegestowe on þone folchearpað þæt up ondlang þæs hearpoðes to þæm Criste mæle.
And swa fram þam Cristes mæle of dun weard ondlang anre ealdre dic west weard & norð weard þæt in ælr broc.
And seoððan a swa alr broc ligeð upweard to mos setena gemære.
And swa big mos setena gemære ofer siht ferð on þone ealdan kyninges hagan.
Þæt swa andlang þæs aldan cyninges hagan norð weard to ðam aldan stodfalde.
And þonne fram ðam aldan stodfalde bi beonot setena gemære on sihferð.
And swa ondlang sihtferdes in bæle.
Ðis syndon ðæs londes gemære æt mosleage of ðæm aldan felda westreht on gearnec.
Swa ondlang broces on ðone gemærhagan ofer fildburnan on timberrycg.
Ðonon on beostinghrycg swa eastweard on blacan brygce.
Þanon eft on þone ealdan feld.
